        <p>
            I am Namanita Anand a Fine arts teacher by passion, and a art and craft teacher. I was born in Delhi NCR INDIA. I take online workshops for Kids to learn and have fun, And for Working people and senior citizens max age of 70 for relaxation. I also design fabric jwellery and sell them.

            I take colouring with paints, coffeee, crayons etc workshops. Every month it's different. I even take special art workshops for the weekends.
            If you want to enroll your kid in such workshops you can just go to the contacts section and you can whatsapp me for a callback.

            If you want to see my designing of fabric jwelery you can go to the contacts section and open my Facebook and Instagram page.

            If you want to see the type of artworks or the fabric jwelery designing I do then you can go to the Images and videos section.

            If you want to see the work my students do in my art workshops or the art classes you can go to the work section.

